Package org.shared.image.filter

A package of two-dimensional filters.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DerivativeOfGaussian
    An implementation of DooG filters up to 0th and 1st derivatives.
    Filters
    A static utility class in support of two-dimensional filters.
    Gabor
    An implementation of oriented, complex-valued Gabor filters.
    GaborCircular
    An implementation of circular, complex-valued Gabor filters.
    LaplacianOfGaussian
    An implementation of LoG filters.
    Mean
    A mean low-pass filter.
